							Software engineer with experience in full-stack
							development using technologies like JavaScript and Java.
							Constantly learning to solve problems both
							professionally and personally.
						</p>
						<p class="text-[#F0F0F0] max-w-140 md:text-2xl mt-10">
							I have developed strong skills in
							teamwork, problem-solving, and independent learning, which
							enable me to adapt easily to new academic and professional
							challenges.
						</p>

						<div class="flex flex-row gap-10 mt-10 max-md:justify-center max-md:items-center">
